      "updated": 1773766283225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Now draw the diagram. Walk the interviewer\nthrough a full request: \"User hits the API\n→ load balancer → app server → check\nRedis → if miss, hit DB → return redirect.\"\nName your tech choices and explain why —\n\"Redis because lookups are read-heavy and\nlow-latency is critical.\" This is where most\nof the interview time goes.",
      "fontSize": 32.638910186418826,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Now draw the diagram. Walk the interviewer through a full request: \"User hits the API → load balancer → app server → check Redis → if miss, hit DB → return redirect.\" Name your tech choices and explain why — \"Redis because lookups are read-heavy and low-latency is critical.\" This is where most of the interview time goes.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
