      "seed": 2010352746,
      "version": 1146,
      "versionNonce": 601314806,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774506493366,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1) Intitial API to Upload files will now change to 3 three process\n- POST /files/presigned_url -> PresignedURL\n{\n    FileMetaData\n}\n- use PresignedURL to upload file via PUT request to Blob Storage from\nclient \n- Once Uploaded on s# Notification will be triggered and will update the\nstatus in our Metadata ",
      "fontSize": 20.404343903454187,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1) Intitial API to Upload files will now change to 3 three process\n- POST /files/presigned_url -> PresignedURL\n{\n    FileMetaData\n}\n- use PresignedURL to upload file via PUT request to Blob Storage from client \n- Once Uploaded on s# Notification will be triggered and will update the status in our Metadata ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
