      "updated": 1774522463932,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Monitor Local folder for changes \n- MACOS : FSEvents\n- Windows : FileSystemWatcher\n2) If change detected locally,, queues modified file for upload\nlocally \n3) Then use upload API to update remote server\n4) Conflicts strategy - last write wins (or versioning)\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Monitor Local folder for changes \n- MACOS : FSEvents\n- Windows : FileSystemWatcher\n2) If change detected locally,, queues modified file for upload locally \n3) Then use upload API to update remote server\n4) Conflicts strategy - last write wins (or versioning)\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
