    {
      "id": "KoukN6Wjc_GEFfJYVy9i2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1678.5683677415668,
      "y": 4118.616235675063,
      "width": 290.39959716796875,
      "height": 400,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#121212",
      "backgroundColor": "#fcc2d7",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bIL",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1118268278,
      "version": 537,
      "versionNonce": 1603790710,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774526537104,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "WHy not single POST request?\n\n1) Web servers and clinet have\ntimeout setting for 50GB file it\neasily exceeds timeout limit\nEx 50GB over 100 Mbps -> 1.11hrs\n50*8 = 400gb ->  400*1000 ->\n400000Mb -> 400000/100 = 4000\nseconds \n4000/60 -> 66.77 minutes\n \n2) Most Brower and server will\nhave limitation on size of\nrequest payload so can't transfer\nsuch big file at once \n\n3) Network Interruption , user\nhave to start from scratch again\n \n4) Very bad user experiecne",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "D3jXPgsWJkul_qvUlbJmh",
      "originalText": "WHy not single POST request?\n\n1) Web servers and clinet have timeout setting for 50GB file it easily exceeds timeout limit\nEx 50GB over 100 Mbps -> 1.11hrs 50*8 = 400gb ->  400*1000 -> 400000Mb -> 400000/100 = 4000 seconds \n4000/60 -> 66.77 minutes\n \n2) Most Brower and server will have limitation on size of request payload so can't transfer such big file at once \n\n3) Network Interruption , user have to start from scratch again\n \n4) Very bad user experiecne",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
